# Packages

Use yarn as the package manager.
Use the latest version of TypeScript.
Use the latest version in 18.x of React.
Use the latest version in 14.x of Next.js.
Use css modules for setting styles.
Use icons from Remix Icon.
Use microCMS and the JavaScript SDK.
Use wrangler, @cloudflare/next-on-pages and other necessary packages to deploy the app to Cloudflare Pages.
Use eslint and prettier to format codes.

# Directory structure

```
src
 |- components
 |  |- features
 |  |- ui
 |     |- Header
 |        |- Header.tsx
 |        |- Header.module.scss
 |        |- index.ts
 |- hooks
 |- pages
 |- services 
 ```